01772" rel="nofollow">1900 1772</a></span></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;"><strong>Email                           </strong>: <a href="mailto:Maylamda@haiau.com">Maylamda@haiau.com</a></span></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</thead>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>', 'Máy Làm Đá Viên Hải Âu HA 60 (60kg/24h)', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'may-lam-da-vien-hai-au-ha-60-60kg-24h', '', '', '2018-07-09 15:24:18', '2018-07-09 08:24:18', '', 0, 'http://localhost:81/haiau/?p=164', 0, 'post', '', 0),
