 href="tel:+84915078989" rel="nofollow">091.507.8989</a></span></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr style="text-align: justify;">\r\n<td><span style="font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;"><strong>Showroom Nha Trang</strong>: Số 131 đường 23/10, P. Phương Sơn – <a href="tel:+842583826899" rel="nofollow">(0258) 3826 899</a> – <a href="tel:+84915078989" rel="nofollow">091.507.8989</a></span></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr style="text-align: justify;">\r\n<td><span style="font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;"><strong>Trung Tâm Bảo Hành</strong>: Số 1 đường CN7, KCN Từ Liêm, Bắc Từ Liêm, HN – <a class="seoquake-nofollow" href="tel:+8419001772" rel="nofollow">1900 1772</a></span></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;"><strong>Email                           </strong>: <a href="mailto:Maylamda@haiau.com">Maylamda@haiau.com</a></span></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</thead>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>', 'Máy Làm Đá Viên Hải Âu HA 180', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'may-lam-da-vien-hai-au-ha-180', '', '', '2018-07-09 15:27:46', '2018-07-09 08:27:46', '', 0, 'http://localhost:81/haiau/?p=170', 0, 'post', '', 0),
